attributes.title: PSA AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH
attributes.review: I downloaded this app to support our lord and savior Donald J Trump, but shortly after it was downloaded I began to notice some strange goings on. I opened the app and gave it all my information, and I was beginning to peruse the app itself, when I heard a loud crash coming from my kitchen. I went to the kitchen, and I found a bag full of TRUMP 2020 face masks filled with rocks had been thrown through my kitchen window. This was not a problem, as when you sign into the app it says they will be delivered, but the real issue was that in the corner of my kitchen the tank that housed my goldfish was suddenly mysteriously empty! This app stole my goldfish!!! I don’t care about the election, or the app, or anything anymore. All I want.......... is to get Mr. Bubble back. Please, just send back Mr. Bubble.

attributes.title: Nastiest Cheeto Bag EVER‼️‼️‼️
attributes.review: I opened the app to find out that it was LESS than halfway full. I mean as you’d expect from a lays company chip bag it’s not all the way full so the chips don’t crush during shipping, and instead are usually halfway or a little more full. However I opened this expired app with a dusty Cheeto from 1945 on the front page. I thought “huh that’s weird” but proceeded to sign up as normal. Only to find the app/bag LESS THAN HALFWAY FULL!!!! There were a total of 3 Cheetos. Much disappointed, could’ve been better. Did not live up to all of the fake news and hype. Then I find the NUDES of the Cheeto from 1945 in one of the tabs, I was mortified. As a minor I must say that seemed pretty illegal. Sad to hear about the death of the pres tho, hope the families taking it ok.
